Package: fdesigns
Type: Package
Title: Optimal experimental designs for functional models depending on profile factors using the coordinate exchange algorithm
Version: 1.0
Date: 2022-08-22
Author: Damianos Michaelides
Maintainer: Damianos Michaelides <dm3g15@soton.ac.uk>
Description: Optimal experimental designs for functional linear and functional generalised linear models, for scalar responses and profile/dynamic factors. The designs are optimised using the coordinate exchange algorithm. 
License: GPL-2
Imports: Rcpp, Matrix, parallel, mvQuad, mvtnorm
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
